channel.title: Gustav Janssons devlog
channel.description: This blog is a try to me keep motivates and a way to see my progress on my current projects. Let’s see how it goes!

item.title: Week 30
item.description: This week was spent on configuring arch and irl stuff. Not much fel work I’m afraid :(

item.title: Week 29
item.description: This week I started/restarted my scripting language from scratch.

item.title: Week 28
item.description: This week I didn’t do much either but I just started a 3 week vacation, and I’m expecting at least some coding to be done.

item.title: Week 27
item.description: I didn’t do much this week either. Shame on me. Added a issue detailing strings over multiple rows.

item.title: Week 26
item.description: This week I mostly spent researching raspberry pi and 3d printing.

item.title: Week 25
item.description: This week I celebrated midsumer with friends. Nothing really happened codewise.

item.title: Week 24
item.description: This week I mostly watched netflix again. I really need to finish the extended json part of my json reader so I can use it in my own projects.

item.title: Week 23
item.description: This week I added some cases on github for my json parser, but most of my time was spent on irl stuff.

item.title: Week 22

item.title: Week 21
item.description: This week I added some more tests, and added coverage. Turns out that even if you think you have 100% you dont’t.

item.title: Week 20
item.description: This week I didn’t work on the json reader as I was supposed to. Instead I worked on my bezier editor. Ideally I want the json reader complete before the end on may and a stable API a week before, so by the end of next week…

item.title: Week 19

item.title: Week 18

item.title: Week 17
item.description: This week I spent on improving my command line argument parser, though I noticed at the end of the week I might be able to replace my code with a library.

item.title: Week 16
item.description: This week I mostly spend on maze generation. I implemnted 2 maze generation algorithms and one cave generator.
